      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it in pristine shape, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'd love to show it off!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
