      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen exhibits zero VANOS rattle and a perfectly linear torque curve. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The suspension retains original damping characteristics with no bushing deformation or chassis fatigue. Finished in concours-level paint with an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this is a turn-key example for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
